input: 슈퍼히어로가 하늘을 날자 사람들의 시선이 집중되는 장면을 만들어줘

input: 갑자기 비가 쏟아져 모두가 뛰어가는 도심의 모습을 영상으로 만들어줘

allResults: [{'optimizedPrompt': 'A group of office workers in business attire of various ages and appearances, running urgently through a rain-soaked city street in front of modern office buildings. The sky is covered with dense, dark clouds and raindrops are visibly falling, hitting the ground and creating clear reflections on the wet pavement. The camera tracking shot follows the rushing workers from a medium-wide angle, capturing expressions of urgency and concern on their faces as they avoid slipping and dodge puddles.
